    "RecipeStep": {
      "description": "recipe の 1 ステップ。\n\nv0.5.0-rc1 から下記のステップ型をサポート:\n- **command step**: `command` を指定 (従来通り)、機器コマンドを実行\n- **wait step**: `wait: { seconds: N }` を指定、N 秒待機\n\nv0.5.1 で polling 系を追加:\n- **wait_until step**:        `wait_until: { timestamp: ... | seconds_from_now: ... }`\n- **wait_for_condition step**:`wait_for_condition: {...}`\n- **wait_for_stable step**:   `wait_for_stable: {...}`\n\nいずれか一つを必ず指定する (複数指定はエラー)。\n\nYAML 例:\n    steps:\n      - { command: \"set_voltage\", args: { voltage: 5 } }\n      - wait: { seconds: 60 }\n      - wait_for_stable:\n          instrument: temp1\n          command: measure_temperature\n          tolerance: 0.2\n          window_s: 60\n          interval_s: 5\n          timeout_s: 1800\n      - { command: \"measure_temperature\" }",
      "properties": {
        "command": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Command"
        },
        "args": {
          "additionalProperties": true,
          "title": "Args",
          "type": "object"
        },
        "result_as": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Result As"
        },
        "description": {
          "default": "",
          "title": "Description",
          "type": "string"
        },
        "instrument": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Instrument"
        },
        "stagger_ms": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "type": "integer"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Stagger Ms"
        },
        "wait": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "additionalProperties": true,
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Wait"
        },
        "wait_until": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "additionalProperties": true,
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Wait Until"
        },
        "wait_for_condition": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "additionalProperties": true,
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Wait For Condition"
        },
        "wait_for_stable": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "additionalProperties": true,
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Wait For Stable"
        },
        "barrier": {
          "anyOf": [
            {
              "additionalProperties": true,
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "type": "null"
            }
          ],
          "default": null,
          "title": "Barrier"
        }
      },
      "title": "RecipeStep",
      "type": "object"
